   489 				; turn the cursor on
   490 				; normally, the screen windows starts in a state of all 0.
   491 				; that is fine for the characters
   492 				; but for the colors, this means the overlay bit is not set
   493 				; so all the colors are transparent and the cursor doesn't show up right
   494 				; so we clear the page first, which fills the page with null and the default color
   495 2933 20 AC 2C				jsr	scroll_page
   496 2936 20 D8 2C				jsr	cursor_on
